'''熊貓雲端防毒軟體'''是[[熊貓安全公司|熊貓安全公司]]推出的[[防毒軟體|防毒產品]]之一，分免費版和付費版兩種版本。它是一個基於[[雲端運算|雲端技術]]的軟體，也就是說，檔案掃描在遠端的伺服器上進行，而不會佔用使用者電腦的資源。熊貓安全公司的「集體智慧」（Collective Intelligence）技術是該軟體的基礎<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/en/25.htm |title="What is Collective Intelligence" |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2009-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090807012428/http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/en/25.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。該軟體可以執行手動的系統掃描，或持續在背景常駐以提供即時保護對抗病毒和惡意網站，但也會稍微拖慢系統速度<ref name="april2009">[http://www.thetechherald.com/article.php/200918/3565/Review-Panda-Cloud-Antivirus Review: Panda Cloud Antivirus] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thetechherald.com/article.php/200918/3565/Review-Panda-Cloud-Antivirus |date=20090703153633 }} Steve Ragan, techherald.com 2009-4-29</ref>。

目前該軟體已改名為「熊貓免費防毒軟體」，分免費版和專業版兩種版本。免費版提供實時防病毒與防窺視功能；專業版則包含免費版的所有功能外，另外含有防火牆、WIFI保護和VIP支援。專業版一年份售價43.99美元。

== 功能 ==
熊貓安全公司表示，熊貓雲端防毒軟體可偵測病毒、特洛伊木馬程式、蠕蟲、間諜軟體、撥號器和駭客工具，並攔截駭客入侵和其他安全風險<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/en/120.htm |title="What type of threats does the antivirus detect?" |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2020-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712180118/http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/h_en/120.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

熊貓雲端防毒軟體依靠熊貓安全公司的「集體智慧」技術和其雲端的最新資訊來運作<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/en/140.htm |title="What is the cloud?" |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2009-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090807012229/http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/en/140.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該軟體通常需要[[互联网|網際網路]]連線以存取這些最新資訊；當電腦未連線到網際網路時，它會使用「目前最流行威脅」的暫存資訊來保護電腦<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/en/145.htm |title="What happens if my computer is not connected to the Internet?" |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2009-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090827225611/http://www.cloudantivirus.com/help/01/en/145.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。自1.4版起，該軟體工具列和網站過濾功能開始支援Internet Explorer 9 和Firefox 4。

== 評測 ==
一份2009年4月的評測報告認為熊貓雲端防毒軟體1.0版快速、簡單、介面清爽且易於上手，偵測率也相當不錯<ref name="april2009"/>。該份報告顯示其惡意軟體與惡意連結的偵測率皆達100%<ref>{{cite web |author=James Wray and Ulf Stabe |url=http://www.thetechherald.com/article.php/200918/3565/Review-Panda-Cloud-Antivirus?page=1 |title=Review: Panda Cloud Antivirus - Security |publisher=Thetechherald.com |date=2009-04-29 |accessdate=2010-11-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722190711/http://www.thetechherald.com/article.php/200918/3565/Review-Panda-Cloud-Antivirus?page=1 |archivedate=2011-07-22 }}</ref>。

當1.0版於2009年11月10日推出時，PC Magazine對熊貓雲端防毒軟體進行評測，並給它「防毒軟體最佳選擇獎」(Editor's Choice Award for Best AV)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2355827,00.asp |title=PC Magazine: Panda Cloud Antivirus  Edition 1.0 Editor's Choice |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2015-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904233236/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2355827,00.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在Tech Radar的評測中寫道：「我們認為最好把熊貓雲端防毒軟體視為一項預防惡意軟體的工具，而非一項用來清理已受感染系統的工具。」(We think that Panda Cloud Antivirus is best viewed as a defense
tool rather than a utility for cleaning up a system that's already riddled with
infection.)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.techradar.com/reviews/pc-mac/software/utilities/anti-malware-software/panda-cloud-anitvirus-674644/review |title=Panda Cloud Antivirus approaches virus protection from a different angle |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2010-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100412200248/http://www.techradar.com/reviews/pc-mac/software/utilities/anti-malware-software/panda-cloud-anitvirus-674644/review |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Lifehacker的評測中說道，該防毒軟體對系統負擔很輕，而且這種對抗惡意軟體的方式相當創新。然而它們並未使用任何真正的惡意軟體進行測試(只使用了追蹤cookies)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lifehacker.com/5234347/panda-cloud-antivirus-is-a-lightweight-always+updated-virus-killer |title=Panda Cloud Antivirus is a Lightweight, Always-Updated Virus Killer |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2013-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605062000/http://lifehacker.com/5234347/panda-cloud-antivirus-is-a-lightweight-always+updated-virus-killer |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

Softpedia的評測說熊貓雲端防毒軟體擁有很高的偵測率，但沒有完整顯示出其偵測結果。整體上他們認為該軟體易於使用，介面清爽，是市場上輕度使用者的最佳選擇<ref>[http://www.softpedia.com/reviews/windows/Panda-Cloud-Antivirus-Review-126499.shtml Panda Cloud Antivirus Goes Final Cloud-based Panda protection] {{Wayback|url=http://www.softpedia.com/reviews/windows/Panda-Cloud-Antivirus-Review-126499.shtml |date=20150924122353 }}.</ref>。

== 授權許可 ==
免費版的熊貓雲端防毒軟體只允許在[[公立學校|公立學校]]、非政府組織、非營利組織，和個人家庭中使用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://softwareula.wordpress.com/2010/07/20/panda-cloud-antivirus/ |title=Panda Cloud AntiVirus {{!}} Software EULA's Blog |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305145312/https://softwareula.wordpress.com/2010/07/20/panda-cloud-antivirus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

